This product wraps and redistributes the upstream Grafana MCP server:

  Grafana MCP Server (mcp-grafana)
  https://github.com/grafana/mcp-grafana
  Copyright 2024-2026 Grafana Labs
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0

The container image grafana/mcp-grafana, pulled from Docker Hub at the
version pinned in docker/Dockerfile, is included verbatim in our wrapper
image as the executable layer. We do not modify upstream binaries — only
the entrypoint, healthcheck, and base packages.

Other notable bundled software (run-time only, included via Compose for
local development; NOT part of the production wrapper image):

  Grafana OSS (grafana/grafana-oss)            — AGPL v3
  Prometheus (prom/prometheus)                 — Apache-2.0
  Grafana Loki (grafana/loki)                  — AGPL v3
  Grafana Tempo (grafana/tempo)                — AGPL v3
  Grafana Pyroscope (grafana/pyroscope)        — AGPL v3
  MCP Inspector (@modelcontextprotocol/inspector) — MIT

Each component remains under its own license. This repository does not
relicense any of them.
